{"word":"G4834 - συμπαθέω - sympathéō - soom-path-eh'-o - Have compassion","slug":"G4834","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμπαθέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sympathéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soom-path-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Have compassion"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - sumpatheo&#x0304;</b> - <i>soom-path-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4835\">G4835</a>; to <i>feel</i> &ldquo;sympathy&rdquo; with, that is, (by implication) to <i>commiserate:</i> - have compassion, be touched with a feeling of."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2552\">G2552</a>, <a href=\"#/G2553\">G2553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3356\">G3356</a>, <a href=\"#/G3663\">G3663</a>, <a href=\"#/G3804\">G3804</a>, <a href=\"#/G3805\">G3805</a>, <a href=\"#/G3806\">G3806</a>, <a href=\"#/G3958\">G3958</a>, <a href=\"#/G4236\">G4236</a>, <a href=\"#/G4310\">G4310</a>, <a href=\"#/G4777\">G4777</a>, <a href=\"#/G4835\">G4835</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>"}]}